Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:10.49,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:19.16,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:31.46,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:52.03,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't this just messed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:57.41,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I have to get kicked out?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:01:02.42,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I have more magical power than the royals do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:08.33,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Magic is everything in \Nthis world... isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:15.88,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,This is a load of bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.98,0:01:20.09,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.73,0:01:23.14,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.72,0:01:25.34,main,Valtos,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:32.61,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I'll show the Clover Kingdom's \NMagic Knights the true extent of my powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:52.71,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I would always close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:57.05,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And cower at reality
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:02:01.72,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:06.10,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Of just making excuses to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:07.25,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand right there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:08.40,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be near you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:09.54,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Any minute now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:12.90,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait right there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:12.90,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(The decisive battle is still a long way off)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:14.98,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Black and blue
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:20.91,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give up on giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:24.41,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And get the world on my side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:28.09,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the reason I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:33.29,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time somewhere under this sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:39.18,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Break through the tearful nights
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:42.43,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And head where the light shines
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:46.27,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep my promise
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:49.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:53.36,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,shape of love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:01.55,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Capital Riot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:09.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to run from these jerks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:12.08,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:19.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Calling us peasants, rats, \Nembarrassments, failures...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:23.43,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if you think we're worthy or not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:26.18,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch! I'm going to—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:30.26,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, you scoundrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:33.10,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't even be allowed to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:34.13,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:36.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:38.62,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,He just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:41.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:44.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to pile up merit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:47.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,become the Wizard King,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:49.20,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,and shut you all up!
