Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:03.72,sign_5760_52_Alecdora,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Alecdora
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:03.72,sign_5760_53_Hamon,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Hamon
