Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:07.22,sign_5844_55_Nozel,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Nozel
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:07.22,sign_5760_53_Hamon,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Nebra
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:09.66,sign_5928_57_You_fool_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,You fool
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:11.86,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A-Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:15.69,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:18.23,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Become...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:20.11,main,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,...the Wizard King?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.20,main,Solid and Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make us laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:32.25,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Water Binding Magic: Sea Serpent's Coils!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:43.59,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:47.76,main,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,Mist Binding Magic: Mist Spider's Threads.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:02.97,italics,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:04.70,italics,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,He's erasing the magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:09.45,italics,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,He's no ordinary peasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:10.81,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:14.95,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,If that's his attack range, \Nthere's no reason for concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:19.75,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Sand Creation Magic: Sand-Armored Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:30.51,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,A-Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:33.14,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:34.64,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:37.31,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:43.60,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,To act in such a way at a festive occasion\Nlike the decoration ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:45.32,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,You will surely be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:51.01,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:54.83,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Why so soft, Golden Dawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:06:00.13,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone that self-confident \Nneeds to be taught a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:02.34,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:04.92,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,So that they can never talk back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.63,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Solid, please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:09.64,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Water Bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.01,0:06:14.35,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:21.69,flashback,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,You're such an embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:31.37,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,to Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:48.72,italics,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just make me kneel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:51.72,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,You lowly peasant!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:57.18,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not holding back anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.49,0:06:59.97,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Solid, p-please, no more...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:23.42,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Nozel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:30.17,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Solid, don't be so quick to use \Nyour magic on a mere peasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.47,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:32.87,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:35.93,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Do you plan to shame the Silva family?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:41.05,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What is this chill in the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:45.83,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cold pressure that's \Ndifferent from Captain Yami's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:50.97,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Captain of the Silver Eagles?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:55.63,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,A peasant that foolishly tried to\Ndefy royalty... How shall I punish you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:05.17,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What should I do?\NAt this rate, Asta will...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.67,0:08:13.51,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:20.43,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting so worked \Nup over a little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:22.81,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You should be ashamed of yourself, Silvas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:31.86,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as Mimosa said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:34.53,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite amusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:36.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:41.34,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,All right, rejoice! I, Leopold Vermillion,\Ndeclare you my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:44.71,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:48.09,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,What was your name? Casta?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:51.10,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Leopold, it's Asta. He's Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:55.53,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, eh? That's a great name, my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:57.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rival?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.18,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Come, now! Rejoice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:02.72,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Rejoice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:05.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:09.19,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Vermillion...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:13.07,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Leopold and Fuegoleon are my cousins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:24.12,sign_13261_133_Silva_Family,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Silva Family
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:24.12,sign_13261_120_Fuegoleon_s_Moth,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Fuegoleon's\N{\fs14}Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:24.12,sign_13261_121_Fuegoleon_s_Fath,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Fuegoleon's\N{\fs14}Father
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:24.12,sign_13261_122_Mimosa_s_Father,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa's\N{\fs14}Father
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:24.12,sign_13261_123_Mimosa_s_Mother,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa's\N{\fs14}Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:24.12,sign_13261_124_Noelle_s_Mother,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle's\N{\fs14}Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:24.12,sign_13261_125_Noelle_s_Father_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle's\N{\fs14}Father
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:24.12,sign_13261_126_1st_D_______1st_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,1st D.      1st Son
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:24.12,sign_13261_122_2nd_Son,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,2nd Son
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:24.12,sign_13261_128_1st_Son______1st,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,1st Son      1st D.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:24.12,sign_13261_124_2nd_D_______2nd_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,2nd D.      2nd Son      1st D.      1st Son
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:24.12,sign_13261_125_Fuegoleon,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Fuegoleon
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:24.12,sign_13261_126_Leopold,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Leopold
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:24.12,sign_13261_127_Mimosa,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Mimosa
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:24.12,sign_13261_128_Noelle,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:24.12,sign_13261_129_S_o_l_i_d,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,S\No\Nl\Ni\Nd
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:24.12,sign_13261_130_N_e_b_r_a,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,N\Ne\Nb\Nr\Na
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:24.12,sign_13261_131_N_o_z_e_l,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,N\No\Nz\Ne\Nl
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:24.12,sign_13261_132_Vermillion_Famil,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Vermillion Family
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:19.20,top,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,My father's older brother is \NFuegoleon and Leopold's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:24.12,top,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Also, my mother's older \Nsister is Noelle's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:26.49,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Too many royals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:27.37,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:33.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Thanks, but my rival's actually \NYuno, who's standing over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.93,0:09:39.23,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,No worries! One can never \Nhave too many rivals!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:40.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:44.94,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Asta! You have a very nice body!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.94,0:09:47.27,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,You are indeed qualified to be my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.62,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let us arm wrestle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:49.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:53.01,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Guys really are dumb, aren't they, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:55.28,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your manners, Sol.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:57.00,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,My bad, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:59.30,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "Captain," Sol.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:01.30,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,My bad, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:02.62,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Sol...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:04.66,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.51,0:10:06.37,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.89,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:09.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Is now really the time for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:13.08,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you holding back? Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:14.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:19.38,italics,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming Leopold's rival...\NAsta truly is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.91,0:10:25.10,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,My, aren't we all so very noisy today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:28.73,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like things have calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:33.23,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,A royal acknowledging a peasant as his rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:44.34,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Julius allowed the boy to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:48.64,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,He may be a peasant, but doesn't \Nhe deserve a little credit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:53.59,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd hear such \Nnonsense from a royal's mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:56.81,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that the Vermillion \Nfamily has gone soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:59.38,main,Noze,0000,0000,0000,,You're a disgrace to us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:01.01,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:03.26,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,How am I, an eagle that soars the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:07.27,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,supposed to give any credit to an \Ninsect that crawls on the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:23.07,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What a tremendous clash of mana!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:25.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,H-Holy crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:26.54,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,You can feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:31.62,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can't feel their mana,\NI can tell... that this is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:39.57,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we stop them, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:42.95,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,This is foolish. Ignore the men \Nand their boorish fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:44.61,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Also, call me "Captain."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.61,0:11:46.60,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:48.31,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Call me—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:54.30,main,Messenger,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:11:59.53,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.91,0:12:01.32,main,Messenger,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:03.67,main,Messenger,0000,0000,0000,,The capital is under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:12:58.87,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:13:01.76,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy, destroy, destroy, destroy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:08.55,main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:20.46,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy all the fools who \Ncan't understand my worth!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:34.16,main,Minion A,0000,0000,0000,,Such disgusting creatures. \NWhere did they come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:37.21,main,Minion B,0000,0000,0000,,You must not value your lives, if you're\Ninvading the royal capital like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.14,0:13:45.27,main,Minion C,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:48.09,main,Minion B,0000,0000,0000,,They keep coming toward us even \Nwhen we shoot their limbs off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:49.35,main,Minion A,0000,0000,0000,,Do not falter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:51.01,main,Minion A,0000,0000,0000,,Protect the Clover Ki—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:54.52,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to, you scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:59.56,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost, scum! Scum! Scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:03.11,italics,Minion A,0000,0000,0000,,What is this magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:34.06,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You're stronger than me, right? Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.06,0:14:37.33,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Get out here, Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.53,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,The Royal Capital is under attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:48.38,main,Shiren,0000,0000,0000,,Stone Creation Magic: \NStone Model of the World.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:07.65,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,It's... a three-dimensional \Nmodel of the Noble Realm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:09.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.37,0:15:14.10,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Even the voices of the people at \Nthe scene and their magic levels...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:19.04,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Is he lacing the whole area with mana \Nand simultaneously making it visible?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:23.15,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,This is much more advanced than \Nmy Magic Flower Guidepost!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:27.22,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,A force with this much magic appears \Nin five places simultaneously,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:28.43,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,without us noticing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:34.57,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,A formidable spatial magic user must have \Nmade them materialize in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:39.08,italics,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Even then, the guard mages of \Nthe Noble Realm work in shifts,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.08,0:15:42.21,italics,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,constantly keeping a magic barrier in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:45.42,italics,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,It should be impossible to \Nenter with spatial magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:49.39,italics,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Did they analyze the barrier's \Nmechanism and break through it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:52.13,italics,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Or did one of the guard mages betray us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:55.72,italics,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, they must \Nbe phenomenally skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:59.22,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,How should we assign the \Nmembers we currently have?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:01.48,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,First, we need to guard the \Narea around the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.80,0:16:03.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what the heck are we waiting for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:07.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! There are people \Nout there who need our help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:08.78,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:09.86,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:11.45,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you plan to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:16.95,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even know the full situation yet, \Nand you can't sense magic at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:19.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to where it's noisiest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:22.16,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Wha— D-Do you think you're \Nan animal or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:26.41,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:28.69,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see what you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:31.41,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Asta, my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:34.73,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Guys really are dumb, aren't they, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:36.03,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:37.38,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,And call me "Captain."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:42.54,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Leo's still very much a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:45.06,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to thoroughly retrain him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:49.57,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'd rather not take orders \Nfrom me, but listen well, Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:53.71,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go after Leo and that Black Bulls boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:55.82,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,and after I've joined them,\Nwe'll head to the north district.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:16:59.78,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You, Black Bulls girl, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:02.94,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Eagles, I ask that you \Nhead to the central district,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:04.36,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,where the magic is strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:05.35,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:08.57,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Roses, head to the east district!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:11.98,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not take orders from a man, \Nbut I suppose I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:13.94,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:15.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "Captain."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:20.05,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Dawn, split into two teams and head \Nto the west and northwest districts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:23.39,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,We will protect the people of the Nobel Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:24.76,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:28.65,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll just have \Nto save dessert for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:32.13,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,If we fail to protect the royal capital, \Nwe'll bring shame upon the Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:33.90,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Do not let the enemy escape, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:35.45,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:43.90,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Munchy, munchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:50.82,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to get in by following \NAsta and the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:54.07,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like something \Nawful is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:59.33,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,This looks like a job for Charmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:03.54,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,If I do good, I might get the chance \Nto eat even better food!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:08.19,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I smell something delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:11.94,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I have to fuel up before the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:15.53,sign_26181_261_Central_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Central District
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:18.59,main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you're going to get away with...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:21.95,main,Man 3,0000,0000,0000,,What? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.91,main,Man 3,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it to you, just—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:37.55,sign_26181_261_Central_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,East District
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:48.78,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your manners, Sol.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:51.02,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,My bad, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:52.31,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "Captain."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:58.84,sign_26181_261_Central_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Northwest District
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:08.93,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Those who dare to bring chaos upon the \Nkingdom shall perish before my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:40.24,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,These things keep getting \Nup with half-assed attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:41.95,italics,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:52.23,sign_26181_261_Central_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}West District
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:58.82,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we should work off \Nsome calories before dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:03.38,italics,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Fools who disturb the peace of the capital...\NYou shall be eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:08.91,sign_26181_261_Central_District,Sigh,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1, 1037)}North District
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:19.04,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.04,0:20:22.54,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen them before. \NWhat country is that army from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.54,0:20:23.45,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:39.34,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Little girl... Do you like the Clover Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:41.94,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I-I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:47.05,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So please... stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:51.35,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:55.98,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,So the town... the people...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:20:59.40,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,And you, too, little girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:02.19,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:23.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll protect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:48.60,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My dry emotions gaze at the me from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:51.57,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And push me forward
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.57,0:21:53.66,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I can't find a place to go)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.66,0:21:58.89,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the faintest light can \Nstill break through the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.89,0:22:04.39,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And change the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.17,0:22:06.81,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I will keep believing in you)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.81,0:22:09.69,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In this ever-vivid place
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.69,0:22:12.68,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Break free yourself)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:15.53,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to grasp my endless dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.53,0:22:18.19,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a path that I should choose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:20.25,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Do you wanna try? Do you wanna try?)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:23.16,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever it may lead us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:25.65,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Until my life comes to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.65,0:22:28.33,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accept any pain that comes my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.33,0:22:30.35,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(We can try again, we can try again)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.35,0:22:34.71,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't see tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.71,0:22:40.26,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding onto feelings too intense to voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.88,0:22:43.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep screaming them in my heart
