Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.86,0:22:58.31,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.85,0:23:02.86,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Mr. Animal
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.14,0:23:01.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.26,0:23:04.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to where it's noisiest!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.26,0:23:08.03,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Wha— D-Do you think you're \Nan animal or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.81,0:23:10.07,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,An animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.21,0:23:13.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Woof, woof.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.24,0:23:17.07,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,A dog... My, how adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:20.76,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,But a cat might be nice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:22.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Meow, meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:24.35,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,How delightful!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.35,0:23:29.01,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but maybe something \Neven wilder, like a wolf...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:31.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,All men are wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.22,0:23:34.81,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I just can't choose!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:36.65,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.56,0:23:43.65,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,What a creepy enemy! But there's \Nno time to be creeped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.65,0:23:46.93,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect the citizens \Nof the Clover Kingdom!
